        <p style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Every Fort Knox unit is an all-steel shipping container — fully sealed against mice, spiders, dust, and fire. You're not paying less because you're getting less. You're paying less because Fort Knox is locally owned by James Richards with zero corporate overhead, no on-site office lease, and no franchise fees passed on to customers.</p>

